headline: Emerson Schedules First Quarter 2026 Earnings Release and Conference Call
summary: Emerson (NYSE: EMR) will report its first quarter results after market close on Tuesday, February 3, 2026. Emerson senior management will discuss the results during an investor conference call that same day, beginning at 4:30 p.m. Eastern Time, 3:30 p.m. Central Time.
